"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2886\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2886-TW</a>)</p></section><section><p>4. 投信累計買超 2 日的股票<br/>台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)、光寶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2301-TW</a>)、國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)、元大金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2885:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2885\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2885-TW</a>)</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>5. 投信當日 (07) 買超的股票<br/>中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)、台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、日電貿